---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Header } from '../components/layout/Header';
import { FooterCTA } from '../components/layout/FooterCTA';
import { QuoteModal } from '../features/quote/QuoteModal';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | ABC Autosalvage" description="Privacy policy for ABC Autosalvage. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  
  <Header client:load />

  <main class="pt-28 pb-20 px-6">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-3">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white leading-[1.1]">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-4 font-body">Last updated: April 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-primary)]/30 to-transparent mb-12" />

      <div class="space-y-10 font-body text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        
        <p>
          ABC Autosalvage ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our vehicle quote services.
        </p>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <h3 class="text-base font-heading font-bold uppercase text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-2">Personal Information</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            When you submit a quote request, we may collect:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 text-gray-400">
            <li>Full name</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Zip code</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-base font-heading font-bold uppercase text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-2 mt-6">Vehicle Information</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 text-gray-400">
            <li>Year, make, and model of your vehicle</li>
            <li>Vehicle Identification Number (VIN)</li>
            <li>Mileage and condition details</li>
            <li>Photos or descriptions of damage</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-base font-heading font-bold uppercase text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-2 mt-6">Automatically Collected</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 text-gray-400">
            <li>IP address and browser type</li>
            <li>Device information and operating system</li>
            <li>Pages visited and time spent on our site</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 text-gray-400">
            <li>Provide vehicle valuations and purchase offers</li>
            <li>Contact you regarding your quote request</li>
            <li>Schedule vehicle pickup and towing</li>
            <li>Process payment and transfer of ownership</li>
            <li>Comply with Virginia state and federal regulations</li>
            <li>Improve our website and services</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">3. How We Share Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We do not sell your personal information. We may share your data with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 text-gray-400">
            <li>Towing and transportation partners to schedule vehicle pickup</li>
            <li>Payment processors to complete transactions</li>
            <li>Government agencies as required by Virginia law for vehicle title transfers</li>
            <li>Service providers that help us operate our website</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, comply with Virginia state record-keeping requirements, and resolve disputes. Vehicle transaction records may be kept for a minimum of three (3) years as required by applicable law.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 text-gray-400">
            <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
            <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:Angel@abc-autosalvage.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">Angel@abc-autosalvage.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">7. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Our website uses essential cookies to ensure proper functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">8. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>
            Our website may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., Google Maps). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our services are not directed to individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
          <div class="bg-[var(--color-base-surface)] border border-[var(--color-base-border)] rounded-xl p-6 mt-4">
            <p class="text-white font-bold mb-2">ABC Autosalvage</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400">15346 Blue Star Hwy, Stony Creek, VA 23882, USA</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">Phone: <a href="tel:17576331779" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">(757) 633-1779</a></p>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Email: <a href="mailto:Angel@abc-autosalvage.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">Angel@abc-autosalvage.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/5">
        <a href="/" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:text-white transition-colors font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm border-b-2 border-[var(--color-primary)] hover:border-white pb-1">
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>

    </article>
  </main>

  <FooterCTA client:visible />
  <QuoteModal client:load />

</Layout>
